                      "name": "s2p",
                      "fill": "$text-secondary",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "You agree not to misuse the Service or help anyone else do so. You may not: (a) probe, scan, or test the vulnerability of any system or network; (b) breach any security or authentication measures; (c) access or search the Service by any means other than publicly supported interfaces; (d) forge any TCP/IP packet header; (e) interfere with any user, host, or network.",
