                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "At Looply, we take your privacy seriously. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, store, and share your personal information when you use our platform and services. We are committed to protecting your data and being transparent about our practices.",
